author: Tess Owen, Courtney Brooks
title: These Far-Right Fringe Conspiracies Are Driving the Anti-Lockdown Protests
description: This weekend protesters across the country demanded their states reopen. Militias, anti-vaxxers, and QAnon believers were among them.
content:
The culture wars have come for coronavirus, and a mixed buffet of right-wingers including armed militias, Proud Boys, QAnon conspiracy theorists, anti-vaxxers, and Infowars are helping to drive the conversation.
